#counting length of words 4
f = open("first.txt", "r")
for i in f.readlines():
    k = i.split()
    for s in k:
        if len(s) == 4:
            print(s, end=" ")

Curtains forcing their will
against the wind,
children sleep,
exchanging dreams with
seraphim. The city
drags itself awake on
subway straps; and
I, an alarm, awake as a
rumor of war
lie stretching into dawn
unasked and unheeded.
